36
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,760
Phục vụ.

37
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,550
Mang đồ ăn lên đi.

38
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:58,520
Vâng.

39
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:03,176
Sa Sa,

40
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:04,575
nghe mẹ cháu nói

41
00:04:04,575 --> 00:04:06,250
